premise_source_doc_sentence: Selene , portrayed by British actress Kate Beckinsale , is a fictional character and the main protagonist of the Underworld film series .
In Underworld : Endless War , Selene is voiced by Canadian voice actress Laura Harris .

More specifically , she serves as the central character in the films Underworld  (  2003  )  , Underworld : Evolution  (  2006  )  , Underworld : Awakening  (  2012  )  , and Underworld : Blood Wars  (  2016  )  .
Ultima Underworld II began production in April 1992 , shortly after the completion of Ultima Underworld ; and it was developed in nine months .
The fourth film , Underworld : Awakening , is the sequel to Underworld : Evolution and was released on January 20 , 2012 .
